{"tid":892051,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個神級人物刻畫既動漫角色","createTime":"2018-11-06T15:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T15:03:21.000Z","uid":209193,"like":41,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"a0403c76697a29b9998a7f83ed86d51e98c07100","tid":892051,"uid":209193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"進擊的巨人個艾爾文團長真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗應該係動漫入面數一數二最有領袖才能既人物<br />\n<br />\n早期出場<br />\n獻出心臟句野根本完全代表哂佢<br />\n個種果斷既性格 不論代價都要達目的真係好撚型<br />\n當離巨人真相近左一大步個陣 佢個下笑真係又耐人尋味又夠人性化<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dYLXNJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdYLXNJM.jpg&h=c09326d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n奪回瑪利亞牆前對人民個下吶喊又係好好J <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnxvoKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnxvoKs.jpg&h=229e7c31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係好熱血 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(以下劇透漫畫內容)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到最後仲帶出佢原來一直獻出心臟既原因都唔係100%為人類未來 描寫佢因為童年而對巨人真相既個種渴望真係好癲 由背負一堆犧牲左既手下既壓力 到佢真正放棄個人夢想帶兵沖出去引開野巨注意真係好撚神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFjNq0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFjNq0d.png&h=1e8a0819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更加唔洗講之後二揀一變巨人對佢既個種解脫啦<br />\n夠人性化又影響哂日後既劇情發展<br />\n得罪講句, 同火影寧次個類王道漫既無啦啦死 個價值真係相差好遠<br />\n<br />\n諫山大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9f0586801c702884ec62a4b6a6e5b392757fb2","tid":892051,"uid":34293,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁又神"},{"pid":"df5e2e1ad3d446c2cb8277fe7845bb9ef232501c","tid":892051,"uid":209193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed9f0586801c702884ec62a4b6a6e5b392757fb2","tid":892051,"uid":34293,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁又神"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"有冇其他推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"2c17253e88173dd291537a561ae7ea1844fe67d0","tid":892051,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"來栖乃乃"},{"pid":"094963a6203bef8b5beda1d6087797ccaef43c66","tid":892051,"uid":2223,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"零使 約瑟夫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JgduEvs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgduEvs.png&h=b5f904a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"780f1a42979132e14548719e6c5554372f210da9","tid":892051,"uid":7916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:48:30.000Z","msg":"等睇人講岸本親生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c366010aebf822e30fc577b299facb98a6531e","tid":892051,"uid":35667,"like":13,"dislike":52,"score":-39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"神級人物+神作<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/3o6Zt8EnwMccZiajHq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2F3o6Zt8EnwMccZiajHq.gif&h=c1a0c503&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a88478abd5114545e1299287626c64530f9d1ad","tid":892051,"uid":101253,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0